<% if fresh_user?(@user) %>
	Hello, <%= @user.name %>! 

	Your account with IBABAI has just been created.
	Your login: <%= @user.email %>

	To set your password, please click the link below.

	<%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.pas_reset_token) %>

	If you did not request an account with IBABAI, please ignore this message.

<% else %>

	To reset your password, click the link below.

	<%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.pas_reset_token) %>

	If you did not request your password to be reset, just ignore this email and your password will continue to stay the same.

<% end %>